                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Rockhill</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-04-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 13, 1901</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Rockhill reports that to the end of March the war claim of Great Britain is
                    £4,800,000; monthly expenses thereafter, £120,000. <pb facs="0375" n="369"
                        xml:id="pg_369"/> Should occupation be continued until the end of the year,
                    £1,600,000 additional.</p>
                <p>Hopes to get vote next Tuesday on our lump-sum proposition)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
